5. FREE SOFTWARE FOUNDATION (FSF) COMPLIANCE STATEMENT
================================================================================

While this Software is proprietary, AiLydian Technologies respects the 
principles of software freedom and supports the Free Software Foundation's 
mission. This compliance statement addresses FSF guidelines:

a) USER FREEDOM RESPECT:
   - Users have the right to know what software they are running
   - Clear disclosure of proprietary nature and limitations
   - No hidden or undisclosed functionality

b) DEPENDENCY TRANSPARENCY:
   - All open-source dependencies are properly attributed
   - Dependency licenses are respected and maintained
   - No GPL contamination in proprietary components

c) CONTRIBUTION POLICY:
   - Contributions to underlying open-source projects are encouraged
   - Bug fixes in open-source dependencies are shared back to communities
   - Support for open standards and interoperability

d) ETHICAL COMPUTING:
   - No surveillance or privacy violations
   - No malicious functionality or backdoors
   - Transparent data collection and usage policies

